01:36:38.491 --> 01:36:40.826
Listen, Schwartz,
Malkovich is our vessel.

01:36:40.910 --> 01:36:44.913
We're old. We're going to die if
we don't get into him by midni...

01:37:00.555 --> 01:37:02.389
He called our bluff.

01:37:04.601 --> 01:37:05.934
Shit!

01:37:06.519 --> 01:37:09.897
Can't we just go inside the
portal and push Craig out?

01:37:09.981 --> 01:37:11.857
No, he's much too powerful.

01:37:11.941 --> 01:37:15.778
