01:38:38.403 --> 01:38:40.279
I am bad. I am bad.

01:38:40.363 --> 01:38:43.198
I am bad. I am bad. I am bad.

01:38:43.867 --> 01:38:46.201
I am bad. I am bad. I am bad.

