so all could see!

01:39:24.365 --> 01:39:29.203
Little Johnny Malk-o-pee!
Little Johnny Malk-o-pee!

01:39:30.580 --> 01:39:33.165
Wet his pants
so all could see!

01:39:47.305 --> 01:39:49.264
I loved you so much!

01:39:51.017 --> 01:39:54.186
Oh! Why did you have to
hurt me like that?

01:39:54.562 --> 01:39:56.188
I'm sorry, Lotte.

01:39:56.481 --> 01:40:00.484
I guess I loved you, too,
in my way.

01:40:01.069 --> 01:40:04.947
